name: TOGETHER
description: TOGETHER is a syntax crystal that contains the human story of all of us: relationships, love, friendship, breakup, heartache, success, happiness, loss, redemption, acceptance, memory, time, and death. It starts with when you find your love and live your lives happily together through the good and bad. There will be moments of ecstacy and moments of bitterness. There will be a time for celebrations and a time for revelations. There will be a lifetime of pauses and a lifetime of embraces. Eventually someone is going to die. In that time period, someone is still living their life; experiencing new wonders of the day. Discovering more about themselves and then...it's time to come together again.
